content:
Manage your Models on the Supported Models Page

Get more confident in managing your models by bookmarking the Large Language Model topic in Salesforce Help. View platform-supported models for Prompt Builder and Einstein Studio in one place. Identify model depreciation schedules, and learn the steps to migrate from one model to the next.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions with an Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Platform, or Einstein for Service add-on.

When: This page is available the week of July 1, 2024.

SEE ALSO
Salesforce Help: Large Language Model Support
